{"tid":1566511,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中秋佳節，想同大家分享幾首詩⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-09-13T15:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T08:22:05.000Z","uid":167880,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8da5d6d00d98d20ba5fed509f5ca437c94db72","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:23:16.000Z","msg":"秋節月圓人團圓，<br />\n香港動員許心願。<br />\n爭取民主與自由，<br />\n堅持理想及信念。<br />\n<br />\n感天動地香港人，文明優雅展自尊。<br />\n無懼共匪暴威嚇，以柔克剛流水行。<br />\n五大訴求無港獨，和平有序高理性。<br />\n上善若水天意現，水可覆舟葬邪靈。<br />\n<br />\n小河彎彎向南流，流到香江起浪頭。<br />\n共匪魔爪伸香港，毒染法制侵自由。<br />\n港人高貴不可侮，百萬抗爭撼全球。<br />\n高度自治雙普選，不達目的不罷休!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmN79AO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmN79AO.jpg&h=7b7da28d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kkcsp89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkkcsp89.jpg&h=be4f40ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人，中秋節快樂！"},{"pid":"3c5ad5c2f66972faa3e0e5e28cbb045716d5f1b3","tid":1566511,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:23:40.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51d3f677e9f485d4a009b97fb55e7408e6542964","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CpRRQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CpRRQQ.png&h=42cd7e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「光復香港！」（車汪想聽到大家出聲音）"},{"pid":"da489fbd7f229949ad984f11dd4f2b177a8ab2e6","tid":1566511,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"。。。。"},{"pid