g src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"382a344c5961aac33886470ba039a6ed1416d0c6","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2abcbb63d32762e962fc60f12d949097549aca4a","tid":1566511,"uid":166221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"好耐無見過你，之前段野我語氣重左少少，對唔住"},{"pid":"45528086c58ee375170e644005a086819e669b54","tid":1566511,"uid":76632,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:36:30.000Z","msg":"樓主令我詩興大發<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都整返首<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黑夜難遮<span style=\"color: red;\">光</span>滿月， <br />\n天殘月缺又<span style=\"color: red;\">復</span>圓。<br />\n似水流年<span style=\"color: red;\">香</span>城夢，<br />\n縱死不忘五<span style=\"color: red;\">港</span>願。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑夜=港共，難遮光明正大嘅滿月(香港人)；<br />\n天殘=天朝殘暴，月缺復圓=港人散(傘)後再聚；<br />\n似水流年係梅艷芳嘅一首歌，同時代表發夢Be Water；<br />\n就算死都唔會忘記港人五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-b4ndR0SW6Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-b4ndR0SW6Y&d=sKkpDxzP%2F%2Fasg9kKOzx88qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=f91b72e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-b4ndR0SW6Y</a><br />\n梅艷芳 - 似水流年(1984)<br />\n<br />\n望著海一片滿懷倦 無淚也無言<br />\n望著天一片 只感到情懷亂<br />\n我的心又似小木船<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">遠景不見 但仍向著前</span><br />\n<br />\n誰在命裡主牢我 每天掙扎 人海裡面<br />\n心中感嘆 似水流年 不可以留住昨天<br />\n留下只有思念 一串串永遠纏<br />\n<br />\n浩瀚煙波裡我懷念 懷念往<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">外貌早改變 處境都變 情懷未變</span>"},{"pid":"3fc44612dc88cb281834522c7ea28ef145194115","tid":1566511,"uid":167567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好詩好詩"},{"pid":"b0712f7051e233940bb7d4432b1ef87fe82032f8","tid":1566511,"uid":166221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"382a344c5961aac33886470ba039a6ed1416d0c6","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2abcbb63d32762e962fc60f12d949097549aca4a","tid":1566511,"uid":166221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:04:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓主高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:13:25.000Z","msg":"好耐無見過你，之前段野我語氣重左少少，對唔住"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"唔緊啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中秋節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab50f1a8de961de1b312d2b0b0937bf24a8d995","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:07:05.000Z","msg":"寧可一思進，莫在一思停"},{"pid":"8a819335bcbb2a72f0e907a8fcdecee03bc66862","tid":1566511,"uid":12000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51d3f677e9f485d4a009b97fb55e7408e6542964","tid":1566511,"uid":167880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T15:27:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CpRRQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CpRRQQ.png&h=42cd7e73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「光復香港！」（車汪想聽到大家出聲音）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T08:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}